{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/replacing-if-else-chains-with-switch","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Pretvaranje If Else Lanaca u switch","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako imate mnogo opcija za izbor, <code>switch</code> izraz je cesto laksi za pisanje od dugih lanaca <code>if</code>/<code>else if</code>. Sledece:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (val === 1) {\n  answer = \"a\";\n} else if (val === 2) {\n  answer = \"b\";\n} else {\n  answer = \"c\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>moze se zameniti sa:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">switch (val) {\n  case 1:\n    answer = \"a\";\n    break;\n  case 2:\n    answer = \"b\";\n    break;\n  default:\n    answer = \"c\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244e0","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Pretvorite <code>if</code>/<code>else if</code> lanac u <code>switch</code> izraz.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18266,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/replacing-if-else-chains-with-switch"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function chainToSwitch(val) {\n  let answer = \"\";\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n  if (val === \"bob\") {\n    answer = \"Marley\";\n  } else if (val === 42) {\n    answer = \"The Answer\";\n  } else if (val === 1) {\n    answer = \"There is no #1\";\n  } else if (val === 99) {\n    answer = \"Missed me by this much!\";\n  } else if (val === 7) {\n    answer = \"Ate Nine\";\n  }\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return answer;\n}\n\nchainToSwitch(7);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Ne treba da koristite <code>else</code> izraze nigde u editoru</p>","testString":"assert(!/else/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da koristite <code>if</code> izraze nigde u editoru</p>","testString":"assert(!/if/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p>Treba da imate najmanje cetiri <code>break</code> naredbe</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/break/g).length >= 4);"},{"text":"<p><code>chainToSwitch(\"bob\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>Marley</code></p>","testString":"assert(chainToSwitch('bob') === 'Marley');"},{"text":"<p><code>chainToSwitch(42)</code> treba da vrati string <code>The Answer</code></p>","testString":"assert(chainToSwitch(42) === 'The Answer');"},{"text":"<p><code>chainToSwitch(1)</code> treba da vrati string <code>There is no #1</code></p>","testString":"assert(chainToSwitch(1) === 'There is no #1');"},{"text":"<p><code>chainToSwitch(99)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Missed me by this much!</code></p>","testString":"assert(chainToSwitch(99) === 'Missed me by this much!');"},{"text":"<p><code>chainToSwitch(7)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Ate Nine</code></p>","testString":"assert(chainToSwitch(7) === 'Ate Nine');"},{"text":"<p><code>chainToSwitch(\"John\")</code> treba da vrati <code>\"\"</code> (prazan string)</p>","testString":"assert(chainToSwitch('John') === '');"},{"text":"<p><code>chainToSwitch(156)</code> treba da vrati <code>\"\"</code> (prazan string)</p>","testString":"assert(chainToSwitch(156) === '');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"replacing-if-else-chains-with-switch","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/returning-boolean-values-from-functions","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/multiple-identical-options-in-switch-statements","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244e0","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/replacing-if-else-chains-with-switch"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}